                'title' => '{"en":"Can I be both a Freelancer doing work and a Buyer hiring on iJobDesk?","ch":"Can I be both a Freelancer doing work and a Buyer hiring on iJobDesk?"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>No, you cannot be both a freelancer and a client at the same time on iJobDesk.com.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You have to choose whether you work as a freelancer or hire as a buyer when you sign up.<\\/p>","ch":"<p>No, you cannot be both a freelancer and a client at the same time on iJobDesk.com.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You have to choose whether you work as a freelancer or hire as a buyer when you sign up.<\\/p>"}',
