                'id' => 41,
                'title' => '{"en":"Edit \\/ Close \\/ Cancel a Posted Job","ch":"Edit \\/ Close \\/ Cancel a Posted Job"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>You can edit everything about your job posting.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>To edit a posted job:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers menu, and click My Jobs.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Locate the job you want to edit in opening job list and click Edit in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>To close a posted job:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers menu, and click My Jobs.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Locate the job you want to close in opening job list and click Close in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>To cancel a posted job:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers menu, and click My Jobs.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Locate the job you want to cancel in opening job list and click Cancel in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>You can edit everything about your job posting.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>To edit a posted job:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers menu, and click My Jobs.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Locate the job you want to edit in opening job list and click Edit in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>To close a posted job:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers menu, and click My Jobs.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Locate the job you want to close in opening job list and click Close in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>To cancel a posted job:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers menu, and click My Jobs.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Locate the job you want to cancel in opening job list and click Cancel in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
