            1 => 
            array (
                'id' => 47,
                'title' => '{"en":"Save a Freelancer for later","ch":"Save a Freelancer for later"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>Please use the save feature if you find a freelancer you&rsquo;d like to contact at a later date.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To save a freelancer from their profile:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Perform a search and find a freelancer you like. Click the freelancer profile link.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the Save button at the top right.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To access your list of saved freelancers:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers &gt; My Freelancers<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Choose the Saved Freelancers tab<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>Please use the save feature if you find a freelancer you&rsquo;d like to contact at a later date.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To save a freelancer from their profile:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Perform a search and find a freelancer you like. Click the freelancer profile link.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the Save button at the top right.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To access your list of saved freelancers:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers &gt; My Freelancers<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Choose the Saved Freelancers tab<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
                'parent_id' => 7,
                'second_parent_id' => 0,
                'order' => 2,
                'second_order' => NULL,
                'slug' => 'save-a-freelancer-for-later',
