            array (
                'id' => 49,
                'title' => '{"en":"Interview a Freelancer","ch":"Interview a Freelancer"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>Finding the right freelancer for your job is the key to complete a project successfully.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You have to interview freelancers before you hire to save you time and money down the road.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can start an interview by sending a message to a freelancer.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers &gt; My Jobs and locate the job you want in your Open Jobs and click View Applicants in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click Review Proposals and locate the proposal you want to interview.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the Send Message button to contact the freelancer.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Once you complete this process, the applicant is moved automatically to your Interviews Tab for further review. From this point, you can continue communicating through iJobDesk Messages. Or you may exchange contact information and take the interview to another medium, such as email, chat, or telephone.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You have to decide if it&rsquo;s the right match for your project. And please negotiate the terms of the contract before hiring a freelancer.<\\/p>","ch":"<p>Finding the right freelancer for your job is the key to complete a project successfully.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You have to interview freelancers before you hire to save you time and money down the road.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can start an interview by sending a message to a freelancer.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Hire Freelancers &gt; My Jobs and locate the job you want in your Open Jobs and click View Applicants in the Actions menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click Review Proposals and locate the proposal you want to interview.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the Send Message button to contact the freelancer.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Once you complete this process, the applicant is moved automatically to your Interviews Tab for further review. From this point, you can continue communicating through iJobDesk Messages. Or you may exchange contact information and take the interview to another medium, such as email, chat, or telephone.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You have to decide if it&rsquo;s the right match for your project. And please negotiate the terms of the contract before hiring a freelancer.<\\/p>"}',
                'parent_id' => 7,
                'second_parent_id' => 0,
                'order' => 4,
