            1 => 
            array (
                'id' => 53,
                'title' => '{"en":"Manual Time Logging for an Hourly Contract","ch":"Manual Time Logging for an Hourly Contract"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>Freelancers often use the manual time to account for hours on offline tasks such as sketching or making phone calls, for example, or anything that can&rsquo;t be accurately represented on their Work Diary.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Buyers can decide whether or not their freelancers can bill manual time. They can then allow or disallow it on their contract.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>When you hire a freelancer, the &ldquo;Allow freelancer to log time manually if needed&rdquo; checkbox is selected by default. You have to deselect it to disable manual time for your freelancer.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can change it in Workroom of an hourly contract.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Workroom &gt; My Contracts, locate the contract and click the contract.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>In overview tab, you can find Change link in Manual Time.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click Change link to allow\\/disallow manual time.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>Freelancers often use the manual time to account for hours on offline tasks such as sketching or making phone calls, for example, or anything that can&rsquo;t be accurately represented on their Work Diary.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Buyers can decide whether or not their freelancers can bill manual time. They can then allow or disallow it on their contract.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>When you hire a freelancer, the &ldquo;Allow freelancer to log time manually if needed&rdquo; checkbox is selected by default. You have to deselect it to disable manual time for your freelancer.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can change it in Workroom of an hourly contract.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Workroom &gt; My Contracts, locate the contract and click the contract.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>In overview tab, you can find Change link in Manual Time.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click Change link to allow\\/disallow manual time.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
                'parent_id' => 8,
                'second_parent_id' => 0,
                'order' => 1,
                'second_order' => NULL,
                'slug' => 'manual-time-logging-for-an-hourly-contract',
                'type' => 2,
