            array (
                'id' => 70,
                'title' => '{"en":"Getting Started as a Freelancer","ch":"Getting Started as a Freelancer"}',
            'content' => '{"en":"<p>Getting started as a freelancer on iJobDesk is simple.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/signup\\/freelancer\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Sign up<\\/a> link on iJobDesk.com home page. On the signup page, provide your name, email address, username and password. Read our <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/terms\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Terms and Conditions<\\/a> and <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/privacy-policy\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Privacy Policy<\\/a>. Create an account by submitting and then confirm your email address.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Complete your freelancer profile (including skills, portfolio, etc.), which serves as your iJobDesk resume and is your most powerful tool for getting hired.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/search\\/jobs\\" target=\\"_blank\\">find jobs<\\/a> you are interested and submit proposals to the jobs.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You should check the status of proposals, and Messages tab and Notifications tab often.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You are now ready to be a Freelancer at iJobDesk.com!<\\/p>","ch":"<p>Getting started as a freelancer on iJobDesk is simple.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/signup\\/freelancer\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Sign up<\\/a> link on iJobDesk.com home page. On the signup page, provide your name, email address, username and password. Read our <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/terms\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Terms and Conditions<\\/a> and <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/privacy-policy\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Privacy Policy<\\/a>. Create an account by submitting and then confirm your email address.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Complete your freelancer profile (including skills, portfolio, etc.), which serves as your iJobDesk resume and is your most powerful tool for getting hired.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can <a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/search\\/jobs\\" target=\\"_blank\\">find jobs<\\/a> you are interested and submit proposals to the jobs.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You should check the status of proposals, and Messages tab and Notifications tab often.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You are now ready to be a Freelancer at iJobDesk.com!<\\/p>"}',
