                'id' => 85,
                'title' => '{"en":"Change My Name","ch":"Change My Name"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>You must use your real, verifiable name according to iJobDesk&rsquo;s Terms and Conditions.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Note: You are not allowed to transfer accounts from one person to another on iJobDesk.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To edit your name:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to the Accounts menu &gt; Settings &gt; Click &quot;My Account&quot; to edit your name.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>You must use your real, verifiable name according to iJobDesk&rsquo;s Terms and Conditions.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Note: You are not allowed to transfer accounts from one person to another on iJobDesk.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To edit your name:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to the Accounts menu &gt; Settings &gt; Click &quot;My Account&quot; to edit your name.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
