            array (
                'id' => 86,
                'title' => '{"en":"Edit My Account Information","ch":"Edit My Account Information"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>To edit your account information:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to the Accounts menu &gt; Settings &gt; Click &quot;My Account&quot;<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You should provide accurate information about yourself.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Please be careful when you update your account information:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Email address - Please be sure to use an address you check frequently.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>User ID - It cannot be edited. You&rsquo;ve set it up when you registered.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Name - You must use your real, verifiable name.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Address - You must use your real, permanent address.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Country - You must be logged into iJobDesk from the country.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>To edit your account information:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to the Accounts menu &gt; Settings &gt; Click &quot;My Account&quot;<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You should provide accurate information about yourself.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Please be careful when you update your account information:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Email address - Please be sure to use an address you check frequently.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>User ID - It cannot be edited. You&rsquo;ve set it up when you registered.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Name - You must use your real, verifiable name.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Address - You must use your real, permanent address.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Country - You must be logged into iJobDesk from the country.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
