            array (
                'id' => 92,
                'title' => '{"en":"How to Use Connects","ch":"How to Use Connects"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>You need connects to submit proposals for jobs. Required Connects are different, depending on factors such as the size and type of project. When a project is canceled without forming a contract with any freelancer, the Connects used on that proposal will be returned for you to reuse. You don&rsquo;t need to use any Connects in case a buyer invites you to a job.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To check your current connects balance:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Find Jobs &gt; My Proposals.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Your Available Connects balance is shown at the top right.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>How many Connects do I need to submit a proposal?<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to the job you are going to send a proposal.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Required Connects is shown at the top right under the Submit a Proposal and Save buttons.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>You need connects to submit proposals for jobs. Required Connects are different, depending on factors such as the size and type of project. When a project is canceled without forming a contract with any freelancer, the Connects used on that proposal will be returned for you to reuse. You don&rsquo;t need to use any Connects in case a buyer invites you to a job.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To check your current connects balance:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to Find Jobs &gt; My Proposals.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Your Available Connects balance is shown at the top right.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>How many Connects do I need to submit a proposal?<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Go to the job you are going to send a proposal.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Required Connects is shown at the top right under the Submit a Proposal and Save buttons.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
