            array (
                'id' => 95,
                'title' => '{"en":"Use Messages","ch":"Use Messages"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>You can use Messages to communicate and collaborate with the buyers.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>A message room will be created when you chat with the buyer, and all your messages will be saved in the room. You will be notified by email when you receive a message from a buyer.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To send a message:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the Messages menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Find a person you want to communicate and click the person on the left<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Type message in the box and click Send button.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>You can use Messages to communicate and collaborate with the buyers.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>A message room will be created when you chat with the buyer, and all your messages will be saved in the room. You will be notified by email when you receive a message from a buyer.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To send a message:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Click the Messages menu.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Find a person you want to communicate and click the person on the left<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Type message in the box and click Send button.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
                'parent_id' => 17,
