            1 => 
            array (
                'id' => 101,
                'title' => '{"en":"Submit Deliverables to the Buyer","ch":"Submit Deliverables to the Buyer"}',
                'content' => '{"en":"<p>There are a number of file-sharing options out there, and the buyers you work for may have their own way to do it. If you are not sure how your buyer wants you to deliver your work, please get in touch with them to find out.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can always send your deliverables through the iJobDesk Messages.<\\/p>","ch":"<p>There are a number of file-sharing options out there, and the buyers you work for may have their own way to do it. If you are not sure how your buyer wants you to deliver your work, please get in touch with them to find out.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You can always send your deliverables through the iJobDesk Messages.<\\/p>"}',
