                'content' => '{"en":"<p>The iJobDesk desktop app is designed for collaboration on hourly contracts.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Freelancers can use the iJobDesk Desktop App to log time on hourly contracts.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The desktop application is available for recent versions of Windows, Mac, and Linux.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Here come some helpful links:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/downloads\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Download<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/help\\/article\\/install-ijobdesk-desktop-application\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Installation Guide<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/help\\/article\\/log-time-with-the-ijobdesk-desktop-application\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Log Time with the iJobDesk Desktop Application<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n<\\/ul>","ch":"<p>The iJobDesk desktop app is designed for collaboration on hourly contracts.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Freelancers can use the iJobDesk Desktop App to log time on hourly contracts.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The desktop application is available for recent versions of Windows, Mac, and Linux.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Here come some helpful links:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/downloads\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Download<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/help\\/article\\/install-ijobdesk-desktop-application\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Installation Guide<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.ijobdesk.com\\/help\\/article\\/log-time-with-the-ijobdesk-desktop-application\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Log Time with the iJobDesk Desktop Application<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n<\\/ul>"}',
